        </p>

        <blockquote class="pull">
          "Enjoy the quality. Appreciate the craft. Meet the people whose hard work makes it all possible."
        </blockquote>

        <p>
          This isn't a stiff trade show — it's a celebration of cannabis culture, thrown by growers. Enjoy the quality, appreciate the craft, and meet the people whose hard work makes it all possible.
        </p>

        <p>
          Cast your vote and help choose the best of the best.
        </p>
