      <div class="program-blurb reveal">
        <p style="margin: 0;">Come for the whole thing, or pick your day.</p>
        <ul class="program-options">
          <li><a href="https://www.dgctickets.com/event-details-1/dgc-2026" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Friday VIP Dinner</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://www.dgctickets.com/event-details-1/dgc-2026" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Saturday's Dude Grow Cup</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://www.dgctickets.com/event-details-1/dgc-2026" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Sunday's DGC Concentrate Cup</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://www.dgctickets.com/event-details-1/dgc-2026" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">2-Day Pass — Saturday and Sunday</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://www.dgctickets.com/event-details-1/dgc-2026" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Parking — RV and Tent Camping</a></li>
