          <line x1="24" y1="62" x2="52" y2="62"/>
          <path d="M22 26 C 28 29, 48 29, 54 26"/>
        </svg>
        <p class="day-desc">An intimate Friday-night opener. Settle into the land, meet the growers behind this year's entries, and toast the weekend ahead. The most personal night of the festival.</p>
      </a>

      <a class="day-card reveal" href="https://www.dgctickets.com/event-details-1/dgc-2026" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <div>
          <div class="day-no">Day 02</div>
          <div class="day-day">Saturday — June 6</div>
          <h3 class="day-name">Flower <em>Cup</em></h3>
        </div>
        <svg class="day-icon" viewBox="0 0 76 76" aria-hidden="true">
          <line x1="38" y1="38" x2="38" y2="70"/>
          <path d="M38 38 C32 28 31 12 36 4 L38 2 L40 4 C45 12 44 28 38 38 Z"/>
