          <path transform="rotate(-80 38 38)" d="M38 38 C33 30 32 18 36 10 L38 8 L40 10 C44 18 43 30 38 38 Z"/>
        </svg>
        <p class="day-desc">The headline cup. Sample, judge, and rank a curated field of flower from growers across the state. Live music, food from local makers, and the long afternoon you came for.</p>
      </a>

      <a class="day-card reveal" href="https://www.dgctickets.com/event-details-1/dgc-2026" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <div>
          <div class="day-no">Day 03</div>
          <div class="day-day">Sunday — June 7</div>
