          <path d="M30 20 C 30 14, 26 12, 22 10"/>
          <line x1="41" y1="58" x2="56" y2="62"/>
          <path d="M52 62 V 68 H 60 V 62"/>
          <path d="M20 53 C 24 55, 36 55, 40 53"/>
        </svg>
        <p class="day-desc">Sunday belongs to the chemists. A full day of solventless rosin, live resin, and the kind of hash that earns its name. Judge the entries, talk process, take notes.</p>
      </a>
    </div>
