     ============================================================ -->
<section class="compete" id="compete">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-divider">
      <svg class="leaf-glyph" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
        <line x1="12" y1="12" x2="12" y2="22"/>
        <path d="M12 12 C10.6 9 10.5 5 11.5 1.5 L12 0.5 L12.5 1.5 C13.5 5 13.4 9 12 12 Z"/>
        <path transform="rotate(40 12 12)" d="M12 12 C10.8 9.5 10.7 6 11.6 3 L12 2 L12.4 3 C13.3 6 13.2 9.5 12 12 Z"/>
        <path transform="rotate(-40 12 12)" d="M12 12 C10.8 9.5 10.7 6 11.6 3 L12 2 L12.4 3 C13.3 6 13.2 9.5 12 12 Z"/>
        <path transform="rotate(80 12 12)" d="M12 12 C10.9 10 10.8 7 11.6 5 L12 4.4 L12.4 5 C13.2 7 13.1 10 12 12 Z"/>
        <path transform="rotate(-80 12 12)" d="M12 12 C10.9 10 10.8 7 11.6 5 L12 4.4 L12.4 5 C13.2 7 13.1 10 12 12 Z"/>
      </svg>
      <span class="num">04 — Competitors</span>
      <svg class="leaf-glyph" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
        <line x1="12" y1="12" x2="12" y2="22"/>
        <path d="M12 12 C10.6 9 10.5 5 11.5 1.5 L12 0.5 L12.5 1.5 C13.5 5 13.4 9 12 12 Z"/>
        <path transform="rotate(40 12 12)" d="M12 12 C10.8 9.5 10.7 6 11.6 3 L12 2 L12.4 3 C13.3 6 13.2 9.5 12 12 Z"/>
        <path transform="rotate(-40 12 12)" d="M12 12 C10.8 9.5 10.7 6 11.6 3 L12 2 L12.4 3 C13.3 6 13.2 9.5 12 12 Z"/>
        <path transform="rotate(80 12 12)" d="M12 12 C10.9 10 10.8 7 11.6 5 L12 4.4 L12.4 5 C13.2 7 13.1 10 12 12 Z"/>
        <path transform="rotate(-80 12 12)" d="M12 12 C10.9 10 10.8 7 11.6 5 L12 4.4 L12.4 5 C13.2 7 13.1 10 12 12 Z"/>
      </svg>
      <span class="line"></span>
    </div>
    <br><br>

    <div class="compete-head">
      <span class="eyebrow compete-eyebrow">For Growers</span>
      <h2 class="compete-title reveal">Submit <em>your work.</em></h2>
    </div>

    <div class="compete-grid">
      <article class="compete-card reveal">
        <span class="label">Saturday · Flower Cup</span>
        <h3 class="compete-card-title">Enter your <em>flower.</em></h3>
        <p class="compete-card-body">Open to growers across the spectrum — homegrowers, caregivers, licensed cultivators. Submit your strongest jar and let a room full of peers tell you what they think.</p>
        <button type="button" data-modal-open="competeModal" class="compete-card-link">
          Competitor Information
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none">
            <path d="M2 7h10M8 3l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </button>
      </article>

      <article class="compete-card reveal">
        <span class="label">Sunday · Extract Cup</span>
        <h3 class="compete-card-title">Enter your <em>extracts.</em></h3>
        <p class="compete-card-body">Solventless, hydrocarbon, distillate — all welcome at the right altitude. Bring the work that represents your bench at its best, and let it speak for itself.</p>
        <button type="button" data-modal-open="competeModal" class="compete-card-link">
          Competitor Information
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none">
            <path d="M2 7h10M8 3l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </button>
      </article>
    </div>

    <div class="rules-wrap reveal">
      <span class="rules-eyebrow">How it works</span>
      <h3 class="rules-h2">The format <em>in plain language.</em></h3>
      <div class="rules-grid">
        <div class="rules-card">
          <span class="rules-num">01</span>
          <h4>Submit your jar</h4>
          <p>Flower Cup: 1–2oz of your finest, a quart mason jar's worth. Extract Cup: 10g of your bench's best. We can't promise to return the unused portion — submit what you'd be proud to share.</p>
          <span class="pro">Pro tip — more bud, more peers tasting it</span>
        </div>
        <div class="rules-card">
          <span class="rules-num">02</span>
          <h4>Check in early</h4>
          <p>Flower competitors: Friday's VIP party from 3pm (preferred), or Saturday between 10–11am. Extract competitors: Sunday between 10–11am. Don't be early. Don't be late.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rules-card">
          <span class="rules-num">03</span>
          <h4>Numbered, sealed, scanned</h4>
          <p>Each entry is moved into a numbered mason jar — your number stays secret until tasting wraps. Humidity packs welcome on flower. Every jar is swept by the Nasal Ranger for terp enhancement spray. Offenders get publicly named.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rules-card">
          <span class="rules-num">04</span>
          <h4>Cast your tokens</h4>
          <p>Judges receive a glass one-hitter, a lighter, and JR Tokin voting tokens — five for the Flower Cup, three for Extract. Drop tokens into each entry's Recharge bag. Most tokens wins. No cheating.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="rules-meta">
        <div class="rules-meta-row"><span class="rules-meta-k">Saturday Tasting</span><span class="rules-meta-v">12 — 5pm · Main Tent</span></div>
        <div class="rules-meta-row"><span class="rules-meta-k">Sunday Tasting</span><span class="rules-meta-v">11am — 6pm · Main Tent</span></div>
        <div class="rules-meta-row"><span class="rules-meta-k">Service</span><span class="rules-meta-v">Budtenders pour the samples</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

