      <h2 class="tickets-title reveal">Three ways <em>in.</em></h2>
      <p class="tickets-blurb reveal">Pick a single day, judge the whole weekend, bring your work, or set up a table. Camping is on the land — limited spots.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="tickets-grid reveal">
      <div class="tickets-col">
        <span class="label">Attend / Judge</span>
        <h3>Come <em>taste.</em></h3>
        <ul class="tickets-list">
          <li><span>Friday VIP Party</span><span class="day">Jun 5</span></li>
          <li><span>Saturday Flower Cup</span><span class="day">Jun 6</span></li>
          <li><span>Sunday Extract Cup</span><span class="day">Jun 7</span></li>
          <li><span>RV / Camping</span><span class="day">All weekend</span></li>
        </ul>
        <a href="https://dgctickets.com" class="tickets-cta">
          Get tickets
          <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none">
            <path d="M2 6h8M7 2l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="tickets-col">
        <span class="label">Compete</span>
        <h3>Bring your <em>work.</em></h3>
        <ul class="tickets-list">
          <li><span>Saturday Flower Cup</span><span class="day">Entry</span></li>
          <li><span>Sunday Extract Cup</span><span class="day">Entry</span></li>
          <li><span>Day admission & tasting included</span><span class="day">Same day</span></li>
          <li><span>Competitors don't vote in their cup</span><span class="day">Note</span></li>
        </ul>
