          <ol class="cup-steps">
            <li>Purchase a Saturday Flower Cup competitor ticket.</li>
            <li>Complete the competitor entry form — link sent to your email prior to event.</li>
            <li>Submit your entry at the event.</li>
          </ol>
        </div>

        <div class="cup-section">
          <span class="cup-section-label">Entry Requirements</span>
