          <p class="cup-detail">A quart mason jar's worth.</p>
          <div class="pro-tip"><strong>Pro Tip</strong>The more bud you submit, the more people will be able to judge it.</div>
          <p class="cup-warning">We cannot guarantee that we will be able to return the unused portion (if any) of your entry.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="cup-section">
          <span class="cup-section-label">Competition Check-In</span>
          <p class="cup-detail"><strong>VIP Party Friday — preferred</strong>Check in no earlier than 3pm at the venue. If you plan on attending the VIP Party, make sure you've purchased a VIP Party ticket.</p>
          <p class="cup-detail"><strong>Saturday</strong>Check in no earlier than 10am at the venue. Check-in ends at 11am sharp.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="cup-section">
          <span class="cup-section-label">Handling</span>
          <p class="cup-detail">Your entry will be transferred to one of our 1-quart mason jars, lidded and numbered.</p>
          <p class="cup-detail">You're welcome to include a humidity pack with your entry, but it is not required.</p>
          <p class="cup-detail">All entries will be scanned by Nasal Ranger to detect the presence of any terp enhancement sprays. <em class="flag">Violators will be shamed publicly and repeatedly.</em></p>
          <p class="cup-detail">Your jar number remains secret until the conclusion of tasting.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="cup-section">
          <span class="cup-section-label">Tasting &amp; Voting</span>
          <p class="cup-detail">Competition judging runs from <strong style="display:inline; font-size: 1rem; color: var(--ink); margin: 0;">12–5pm</strong>.</p>
          <p class="cup-detail">All judges receive a glass one-hitter and lighter. Budtenders serve samples in the Main Tent.</p>
          <p class="cup-detail">Each judge receives <em class="flag">five</em> JR Tokin voting tokens. Each entry has an associated Recharge bag — drop one or more tokens into the bag to vote for your favorite entries.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="cup-section">
          <span class="cup-section-label">Rules</span>
          <ul class="cup-rules">
            <li>Don't be early.</li>
            <li>Don't be late.</li>
            <li>The entry that collects the most JR Tokin voting tokens wins.</li>
            <li>No cheating.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Extract Cup -->
      <div class="cup-column">
        <div class="cup-eyebrow">Sunday · June 7 · 11am–6pm</div>
        <h3 class="cup-title">Extract <em>Cup</em></h3>

        <div class="cup-section">
          <span class="cup-section-label">How to Enter</span>
          <ol class="cup-steps">
