          <p class="cup-detail">All entries will be scanned by Nasal Ranger to detect the presence of any terp enhancement sprays. <em class="flag">Violators will be shamed publicly and repeatedly.</em></p>
          <p class="cup-detail">Your jar number remains secret until the conclusion of tasting.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="cup-section">
