          <p class="cup-detail">Competition runs from <strong style="display:inline; font-size: 1rem; color: var(--ink); margin: 0;">11am–6pm</strong>.</p>
          <p class="cup-detail">Each judge receives <em class="flag">three</em> voting tokens. Each entry has an associated Recharge bag — drop one or more tokens into the bag to vote for your favorite entries.</p>
